<a href="/akira/dtd/4091-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_4091">A great way to balance the budget&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/9583-4049">nathan.orth5</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">1 day ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">I have a great idea to help balance out the federal budget, avoiding excessive deficits year after year. DON'T WASTE TAXPAYER DOLLARS ON WEBSITES LIKE THIS ONE, where people just waste everyone's time with posts arguing for the legalization of pot and/or other foolish pet projects.<br/><br/>If anyone has an idea worth while, they can call/write their Congressman/Congresswoman as is proper.</div>
