<div id="Idea_4090"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/4090-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_4090">Abolish the Senate and the Presidency&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/9539-4049">gabegabrielsky</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">1 day ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Abolish the Senate and the Presidency.  Make the House of Representatives the sole federal legislative body and make congressional majorities responsible for administrative responsibilities now undertaken by the executive branch.  </div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_4090" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_4090', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2242&topicID=4090')">Comments (3)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_4090"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2242">New Strategies and Techniques</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_4090"></div>
