<div id="Idea_4025"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/4025-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_4025">Outlaw ALL political contributions&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/9033-4049">Michael Dare</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">2 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">Every campaign finance reform bill that has ever existed has done nothing more than limit the amount of the bribes that public officials are legally allowed to accept. It's got to stop. Make it illegal for anyone to contribute anything to a political candidate, period. Also make it illegal for political candidates to use their own money for their campaign. All political campaigns will be paid for entirely by the government, with each candidate receiving the exact same amount. Freed from the burden of fundraising, politicians can actually focus on doing their jobs.</div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_4025" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_4025', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2242&topicID=4025')">Comments (5)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_4025"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2242">New Strategies and Techniques</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_4025"></div>
