<div id="Idea_4004"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/4004-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_4004">Enhance this web site so it's slightly more functional&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/8469-4049">longshot9999</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">2 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">There's a web site called the halfbakery that has been up and running for several years now.  Its main purpose is to bring new ideas and inventions to light.  As with anything of this nature it attracts juveniles with ridiculous suggestions, but it also attracts some of the brightest minds from around the world who represent just about every scientific discipline.  Their ideas are the ones worth reading.  That's beside the point though.  The main point is that over the years the site has evolved to make it easier for novice users to jump right to their area of interest.  This web site might benefit from some of those enhancements.    </div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_4004" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_4004', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2242&topicID=4004')">Comments (1)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_4004"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2242">New Strategies and Techniques</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=website">website</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=improvements">improvements</a>,&nbsp;<a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?mode=tag&tag=navigation">navigation</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_4004"></div>
